\fBanimate\fP are popular programs from the \fBImageMagick\fP
package.  \fBImageMagick\fP runs on Unix, Windows, Windows NT, Macintosh, and
VMS.
.PP
\fBImageMagick\fP also contains the program \fBdisplay\fP, which is a
