Photoshop, etc. for Windows.
See \fB
.UR http://www.gimp.org
http://www.gimp.org
.UE
\&\fP.  And you can
add most of Netpbm's function to Gimp
using 
.UR http://netpbm2gimp.sourceforge.net/
Netpbm2gimp
